    "description": "Social rejection sting—an abrupt felt exclusion that hits as lonely pull plus self-worth sting, with a flash of hurt-anger. Style note: consider adding category 'rejection' for moments defined by affiliation rupture + self-worth pain (distinct from pure shame or pure loneliness).",
