            "failure_message": "Requires a rejection-flavored blend (lonely_yearning or sadness+shame) plus a hurt-anger edge, grounded in negative valence with low affiliation and low self-worth while attention stays engaged. Blocks grief/despair/numbness arcs. Triggers only on a sharp affiliation or self-evaluation drop to capture the sudden sting."
